FBIS4-14696 "drsov064_s_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-064 Daily Report 4 Apr 1994 Georgia Sign Settlement Agreement in Moscow Sign Settlement Agreement in Moscow LD0404070994 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0645 GMT 4 Apr 94 LD0404070994 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [By ITAR-TASS diplomatic correspondent] [Text] Moscow April 4 TASS -- Georgian and Abkhazian representatives signed in Moscow on Monday an agreement on the return of refugees and a declaration on the settlement of the conflict. The signing of the documents which lay a solid basis for settling the long-standing armed conflict became possible thanks to the Russian mediation and UN assistance.
